data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort, space, and convenience in this immaculate 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home. Nestled in the sought-after Tamarron community in Katy and zoned to the highly-ranked KATY ISD, this two-story gem is move-in ready and offers everything you desire for a modern family lifestyle. The property features spacious living areas, modern appliances, and a two-story design with abundant natural light. Tamarron boasts resort-style amenities like a swimming pool, splash pad, fitness center, and serene walking trails around its lakes. Don't miss this opportunity to own a beautiful home in a thriving community. Contact us today for a private tour!
